markets.title: More to Lose streams on May 16, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If More to Lose has above 9 million total streams on Spotify on May 16, 2025 at 10 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Total stream count will be determined using the Spotify desktop app at 10 AM ET, based on the exact number displayed at that time. Any updates or changes after 10 AM ET will NOT be considered. The following song can be found on Artist home page here: https://open.spotify.com/artist/5YGY8feqx7naU7z4HrwZM6?si=Qz1iMaEQRzW-hoXNoABSQQ
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
